#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1185
msgid ""
"Which PayPal buttons (e.g. Pay Later, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, Mercado Pago, "
"Bancontact, etc.) will appear?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué botones de PayPal (por ejemplo, Pagar Después, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, "
"Mercado Pago, Bancontact, etc.) aparecerán?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1189
msgid ""
"The PayPal buttons are shown automatically based on several factors, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"Los botones de PayPal se muestran automáticamente en función de varios "
"factores, incluyendo:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1191
msgid "The buyer’s country"
msgstr "El país del comprador"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1192
msgid "Their device type"
msgstr "El tipo de dispositivo que utilizan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1193
msgid "The funding sources they’ve enabled"
msgstr "Las fuentes de financiación que han habilitado"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1195
msgid ""
"As a result, each buyer may see a different set of buttons. Pay Later "
"options vary by country and may display different buttons."
msgstr ""
"Como resultado, cada comprador puede ver un conjunto diferente de botones. "
"Las opciones de Pagar Después varían según el país y pueden mostrar "
"diferentes botones."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1201
msgid "How can I hide specific PayPal buttons?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo ocultar botones específicos de PayPal?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1205
msgid ""
"By default, all PayPal buttons are enabled. To hide specific buttons, use "
"the <strong>Disable Specific Payment Buttons</strong> option."
msgstr ""
"Por defecto, todos los botones de PayPal están habilitados. Para ocultar "
"botones específicos, utiliza la opción <strong>Deshabilitar Botones de Pago "
"Específicos</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1206
msgid "Example: To hide the Pay Later button on the Checkout Page:"
msgstr "Ejemplo: Para ocultar el botón Pagar Después en la Página de Pago:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1208
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1224
msgid "Go to <strong>PayPal Settings</strong>."
msgstr "Ve a <strong>Configuración de PayPal</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1209
msgid "Find the <strong>Disable Specific Payment Buttons</strong> setting."
msgstr ""
"Encuentra la configuración <strong>Deshabilitar Botones de Pago Específicos</"
"strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1210
msgid "Select <strong>Pay Later</strong> from the dropdown list."
msgstr "Selecciona <strong>Pagar Después</strong> de la lista desplegable."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1211
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1226
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1232
